Odaily Planet Daily News According to Ai Yi, an analyst on the chain, the "ETH high-win rate band whale" deposited 18.04 million USDC margin to Hyperliquid yesterday. The current fund allocation is as follows: 
1x long LDO: holding $3.209 million, with a current floating loss of $43,000;
spot position HYPE: holding $3.18 million;
spot position UBTC: holding $350,000. In addition, a limit order was placed to prepare to increase the position of LDO and UBTC worth $3.915 million. With the 1x long order, it is equivalent to holding three spot targets.
